										<a class="hf-link" href="https://huggingface.co/spaces/Peeaaa-ant/plan2table/tree/main" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="PDF図面抽出アプリのHugging Faceリンク" title="Hugging Faceリンク">
											<img class="service-icon" src={`${assetBase}brand-icons/huggingface.png`} alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-hidden="true" />
										</a>
									</div>
								</li>
								<li>
									<div class="item-row">
										<a class="item-link" href="https://plan2table-production.up.railway.app/me-check" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">機械図と電気図の突合アプリ（Cloud Vision API）</a>
